  "text": "Sewell [CITATION_1] proved that if the deadlock δ is added to BPA * , then a complete finite equational axiomatization does not exist. In [CITATION_2] it has been shown that if sequential composition and iteration are replaced by their prefix counterparts, then six simple equational axioms are complete for this algebra.",
